	heroAlt="An open Bible held against the colors of India"
	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style=\"color: var(--color-ink);\">Yes &mdash; you can read the Bible free online in India right now.</strong> Christianity is India&rsquo;s third-largest faith &mdash; home to roughly 28 million believers &mdash; and the Bible is legal to own and read here. The <a href=\"https://fathersheartbible.com/read\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">Father&rsquo;s Heart Bible&trade;</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on any phone, with no app to install and no account to create. India is home to the world&rsquo;s second-largest English-using population, so for hundreds of millions of readers it is available today &mdash; and Hindi is among the first new translations on our roadmap. Whether you&rsquo;re searching for &ldquo;read the Bible online,&rdquo; a &ldquo;free Bible with audio,&rdquo; or simply where to begin, you can start in the next breath.`}
