	globalHeading="India and the world"
	globalIntroHtml={`India is not only a mission field &mdash; it is a global people and a sending nation. To reach India with the Father&rsquo;s heart is to reach a people now living in nearly every country on earth, and a church poised to carry it across Asia. This is why reaching India has long been considered strategic for the whole world.`}
	globalStats={[
		{ value: '~35 million', label: "the world's largest diaspora — Indians living in nearly every nation" },
		{ value: '600M+ & ~90M', label: 'Hindi and Tamil speakers spread across the globe' },
		{ value: 'Gateway to Asia', label: 'long seen as strategic for reaching the whole continent' },
	]}
	globalBlocks={[
		{ heading: 'The world’s largest diaspora', bodyHtml: `About <strong>35 million people of Indian origin</strong> live abroad &mdash; the United States (4.5M), the UAE (3.5M), Saudi Arabia, the UK, Canada, and Australia among them. In American tech hubs like North Carolina&rsquo;s Research Triangle &mdash; towns such as Morrisville &mdash; Indian-Americans are among the largest communities. A Bible that speaks to India speaks to a people woven into the whole world.` },
		{ heading: 'Languages that crossed oceans', bodyHtml: `Hindi (600M+) and Tamil (~90M) are spoken far beyond India &mdash; in Sri Lanka, Singapore, Malaysia, Mauritius, Fiji, the Gulf, and across the Western diaspora. To translate India&rsquo;s languages is to reach them on every continent.` },
		{ heading: 'Strategic for all of Asia', bodyHtml: `Preaching in India in 1972, <strong>Billy Graham</strong> said: &ldquo;One out of every six people in the world is an Indian&hellip; and someone has said, <em>As India goes, all Asia will go with her</em>.&rdquo; Reach India, and the door opens to a continent &mdash; few nations are as pivotal to the spread of the Father&rsquo;s heart.` },
		{ heading: 'As India receives, India sends', bodyHtml: `India is home to one of the fastest-growing churches on earth. As India receives the Father&rsquo;s Heart Bible&trade;, Indian believers and the global diaspora are positioned to carry it across Asia and the world.` },
	]}
	wordHeading="His Word will not return void"
	wordBodyHtml={`<p>When our Father said, &ldquo;Let there be light,&rdquo; there was light. His Word does what He sends it to do. In India, Christian orphanages have been closed and ministries pushed out &mdash; yet His Word still advances, for our Father is a back-door Father, and no border can keep Him from His children.</p><p class="mt-4" style="color: var(--color-ink);">&ldquo;My word&hellip; will not return to me empty, but will accomplish that which I purpose.&rdquo; <span style="color: var(--color-muted);">&mdash; Isaiah 55:11</span></p>`}
	verses={verses}
	keepReadingHtml={`Begin with the <a href=\"https://fathersheartbible.com/read\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">whole Bible free online with audio</a>, learn <a href=\"/the-fathers-heart-bible/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">why the Father&rsquo;s Heart Bible&trade; exists</a>, or get oriented with our <a href=\"/guides/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">Bible reading guides</a> &mdash; including <a href=\"/guides/where-to-start-reading-the-bible/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">where to start</a>, <a href=\"/guides/how-to-pray/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">how to pray</a>, and <a href=\"/guides/what-is-the-gospel/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">what the gospel is</a>. Browse Scripture by theme on our <a href=\"/verses/\" style=\"color: var(--color-brand);\" class=\"hover:underline\">Bible verses by topic</a> pages.`}
